Package com.eim.utility.statistics.model

Interface Summary
IStatistics Interface that defines the common getters and setters for a statistic item.
 

Class Summary
BenchmarkDescriptor Object class that describes a benchmark.
Benchmarks do not depend on the entity type they are linked to.
BenchmarkRelatedStatistics POJO representing the benchmark related statistics.

It is annotated with hibernate annotations for persistence purpose.
These statistics are persisted in the table STATS_BENCHMARK and identified using a sequence called SEQ_STATS_BENCHMARK.
ComputedStatistics POJO representing the non-benchmark related statistics.

It is annotated with hibernate annotations for persistence purpose.
These statistics are persisted in the table STATS_COMPUTED and identified using a sequence called SEQ_STATS_COMPUTED.
 

Enum Summary
EntityType An enumeration that lists the available types of entity.
QualityStatus An enumeration that lists the track content and statistics available qualities
StatisticsFrequency An enumeration that lists the available frequencies
